OL,3,CBritish solider dies during training
OL,4,Cexercise in northern Iraq
OL,6,FA British soldier has died during a
OL,7,Ftraining exercise in northern Iraq,
OL,8,Fthe Ministry of Defence (MoD) has said.
OL,10,FIn a statement on Monday, the MoD
OL,11,Fsaid: "It is with deep regret that we
OL,12,Fcan confirm that a training accident
OL,13,Foccurred in northern Iraq on Sunday,
OL,14,F31 May 2026, in which a service person
OL,15,Ffrom the British Army died."
OL,17,FThe MoD said the service member's
OL,18,Ffamily had been informed and that they
OL,19,Fhad requested a "period of grace
OL,20,Fbefore further details are released."
