OL,3,CBritish solider dies during training
OL,4,Cexercise in northern Iraq
OL,6,FThey added: "Our thoughts and
OL,7,Fsympathies are with the family and
OL,8,Ffriends at this sad time."
OL,10,FDefence Secretary John Healey made a
OL,11,Fstatement to the Commons on Monday
OL,12,Fregarding the death, saying: "I know
OL,13,Fthe thoughts of the House will be with
OL,14,Fthe family and with the unit at this
OL,15,Fdesperately sad time."
OL,17,FMore follows...
